{"tid":664597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【星島】惠譽下降香港銀行評級　中港融合　使香港　信貸猛增　樓價急升","createTime":"2018-05-14T07:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T07:56:13.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c4bffec365b5b62b77c90c3e9676af0590fee72e","tid":664597,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.quamnet.com/newscontent.action?articleId=5724420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.quamnet.com%2Fnewscontent.action%3FarticleId%3D5724420&d=H1LxElxrqP%2BjdOOa2Pcn9QKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=51b5203b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.quamnet.com/newscontent.action?articleId=5724420</a><br />\n<br />\n評級機構惠譽因應本港與內地的聯繫更為緊密，下調對香港銀行業經營環境的評估，由「A+」下調至「A」、趨勢穩定。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽指出，隨着中港兩地的經濟和金融體系的聯繫日益加深，令本港的信貸快速增長及樓價急升，均對香港帶來風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1799192&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1799192%26target%3D2&d=H1LxElxrqP%2BjdOOa2Pcn9QKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=d4989a05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1799192%26target%3D2&h=d4398986\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1799192&amp;target=2</a><br />\n<br />\n評級機構惠譽發表報告，下調香港銀行經營環境評級，由「a+/負面」降至「a/穩定」，反映中港經濟及金融融合加深，對本港銀行帶來風險。惠譽又預期本港銀行向內地企業的貸款額將持續增加，憂慮內地一旦發生金融風險，本港也會受牽連。<br />\n<br />\n　　惠譽表示，香港是最受宏觀風險所影響的全球三個市場之一，本港銀行目前信貸增速加快及樓價高企的原因，很大程度上與內地關連性加深所致。"}]}